name: Toddler Table Set
description:
Toddler Table Set

Set includes one table (White only) and four stools (5 colors to choose from). Made in the USA using a combination of high grade Baltic Birch Multi-ply with hand laid Walnut veneer faces, and tough Formica® brand laminate surfaces this table set is sure to withstand the test of time. With a level of style rarely seen in children's furniture the Toddler Table Set is sure to be the envy of parents everywhere.

Don't be the last one on the block to get what's soon to be the hottest table in town.

FREE Shipping in the USA.

Some assembly required.

Specifications: Table 35.5" Square Top x 22" Tall White Formica top surface.

Stools 16" Square x 13.75" Tall your choice of 5 colors.
